metadata.name: Project: Pill Gates
metadata.description:
Decentralized ownership of the "Project: Pill Gates" infoproduct package that is provable & verifiable via the Ethereum blockchain as an ERC-1155 non-fungible token (NFT).

This NFT includes both titles: "Project: Pill Gates" and "Meet Pill Gates" accessible inside the members' area.

More info at https://ProjectPillGates.com

Resale Rights Licenses are exclusively available to Doctor Medici NFT holders at https://DoctorMedici.com
